{"article_id":"PyoUKsNWbDWaZBXu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford said","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"she is `` one hundred percent '' certain","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh is the person","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"who sexually assaulted her","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"when they were teenagers ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"and she told a Senate committee","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that he and his friend laughed at her expense during the attack .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"`` With what degree of certainty do you believe","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh assaulted you ? ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Democratic Sen. Dick Durbin of Illinois asked Ford during a Senate hearing","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that could determine","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"whether the nominee is confirmed to the high court .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Ford also told","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"a nationally televised Judiciary Committee hearing","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"her accusation was `` absolutely not '' a case of mistaken identity .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"the 1982 incident was `` seared into my memory , ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"even though she doesn ' t remember all the details .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who will testify later ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"has strongly denied this and other allegations of sexual misconduct .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"The hearing was the first time","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"the American public saw the person","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"whose accusations had dominated the headlines for weeks ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"having only seen her before mostly in a single grainy photo","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"in which she was wearing sunglasses .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Her nerves were evident ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and her voice cracked during her testimony .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"President Donald Trump was watching the hearing from Air Force One ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders said .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"He hasn ' t talked to Kavanaugh in a couple of days ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"The California psychology professor said","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"the incident has `` haunted me episodically as an adult . ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"She said","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"she was `` terrified '' to testify before the committee","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and that she she `` agonized daily ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"about whether to come forward with her claim .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Ford said","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Kavanaugh ' s friend , Mark Judge , was in the room during the attack","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and that the two were laughing at her .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"she had an `` indelible '' memory of `` the uproarious laughter between the two , and their having fun at my expense . ''","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Sen. Richard Blumenthal brought Ford to tears","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"when he thanked her","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"for coming forward .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"`` If we agree on nothing else today ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"I hope","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"on a bipartisan basis we can agree on how much courage it has taken for you to come forward ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"you have earned America ' s gratitude , ''","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Blumenthal said .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"During a break , GOP Sen. Orrin Hatch told reporters","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that Ford was a `` an attractive , good witness ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"but that it was too early","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"to make a judgment .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"`` I don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"she ' s uncredible . ''","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Hatch said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"he still expects the Judiciary panel to vote on Kavanaugh Friday","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"and expects him to be voted out favorably .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Questioning of Ford proceeded in five-minute chunks","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"with a lawyer","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"hired by Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Rachel Mitchell , alternating with Democratic members of the panel and Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley enforcing the time limits .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Mitchell asked Ford about the atmosphere at the home before the alleged attack .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"`` I can sketch a floor plan , ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Ford said ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that the event was more of a gathering than a party .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Grassley of Iowa called for a `` safe , comfortable and dignified '' proceeding","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"as the panel opened a historic hearing","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that promises to shape the Supreme Court ' s future","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and redefine the `` Me Too '' era .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Kavanaugh said in his prepared statement","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"that he doesn ' t question","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that Ford may have been sexually assaulted by someone ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"but strongly denied","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"that he was the attacker .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"`` I categorically and unequivocally deny the allegation against me by Dr. Ford , ''","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Kavanaugh said .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"`` I have never done that to her or anyone .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"I am innocent of this charge . ''","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"Ford said","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"though they went to different high schools ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"she had been friendly with a classmate of Kavanaugh ' s","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and attended a number of parties","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"that the future judge also attended .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"`` We did not know each other well ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"but I knew him","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"and he knew me , ''","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"Ford said .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"that her husband remembers","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"that she gave Kavanaugh ' s name","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"when the couple discussed the attack in family therapy in 2012 .","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"the attack occurred","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"after she went upstairs","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"to use the bathroom .","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"She said","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"she was pushed into a bedroom and onto a bed","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"and that Kavanaugh got on top of her .","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"Judge was in the room","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"and encouraged the attack ,","depth":16},{"id":106,"text":"she said .","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"`` I believed","depth":17},{"id":108,"text":"he was going to rape me , ''","depth":17},{"id":109,"text":"Ford said .","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"Kavanaugh put his hand on her mouth","depth":18},{"id":111,"text":"to keep her from screaming ,","depth":18},{"id":112,"text":"she said ,","depth":17},{"id":113,"text":"and","depth":17},{"id":114,"text":"because it was hard for her to breathe ,","depth":18},{"id":115,"text":"`` I thought","depth":19},{"id":116,"text":"that Brett was accidentally going to kill me . ''","depth":19},{"id":117,"text":"She said","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Judge ,","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"who has denied any part in such an attack ,","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"jumped on them","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"and she was able to escape .","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"Asked what she remembers from that night ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Ford responded :","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"`` The stairwell , the living room , the bedroom , the bed on the right side of the room","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"as you walk into the room","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"- there was a bed to the right -","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"the bathroom in close proximity , the laughter","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"- the uproarious laughter -","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"and the multiple attempts","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"to escape","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"and the final ability","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"to do so . ''","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"Under questioning from Mitchell ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Ford said","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"she didn ' t know","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"how she got home that night .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"She said","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"the party took place `` somewhere between '' her home and the Columbia Country Club , about seven miles away .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"The Washington Post previously reported","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"she told the paper","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"the party took place near the country club .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"`` Has anyone come forward","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"to say to you ,","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"' Hey , remember ,","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"I was the one","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"that drove you home ' ? ''","depth":15},{"id":147,"text":"Mitchell asked .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"`` No , ''","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Ford responded .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"she didn ' t have her driver ' s license at the time .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"In his opening statement , Grassley said ,","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"`` I want to apologize to you both for the way","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"you ' ve been treated , ''","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"referring to threats","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"made against Ford and Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"after her allegation became public .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"Democratic Sen. Dianne Feinstein thanked Ford for her `` strength and bravery","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"in coming forward . ''","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"The California senator said","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"60 percent of sexual assaults go unreported ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"when women do report them ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"'too often , women ' s memories and credibility are put under assault . ' ''","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"`` This is not a trial for Dr. Ford , ''","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Feinstein said .","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"`` It ' s a job interview for Judge Kavanaugh . ''","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Feinstein said","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"the issue is `` a real question of character for someone","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"who is asking for a lifetime appointment to the Supreme Court , ''","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"and noted","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"that two other accusers came forward in the last several days .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"Kavanaugh is trying to save a Supreme Court nomination","depth":5},{"id":174,"text":"that has become besieged by accusations of decades-old sexual misconduct .","depth":5},{"id":175,"text":"He has strongly denied all the allegations against him .","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"Grassley lamented","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"that the accusation surfaced","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"after his panel held almost a week of confirmation hearings ,","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"while Feinstein accused the GOP of a rush to judgment","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"and complained about a lack of other witnesses .","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"Ford said","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"Kavanaugh tried to remove her clothes","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"and put his hand over her mouth","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"so she couldn ' t scream .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"She is one of the three identified women","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"who have accused Kavanaugh of sexual misconduct","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"but the only one","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"who will testify Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":189,"text":"Republicans are trying to get Kavanaugh , 53 , confirmed as early as next week .","depth":5},{"id":190,"text":"The Judiciary panel has scheduled a vote for Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":191,"text":"and Majority Leader Mitch McConnell has been preparing colleagues for a weekend session","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"that would allow a final vote in a matter of days .","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"Trump said Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"the allegations are `` all false to me ''","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"but added","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"that he could be persuaded otherwise by Thursday ' s testimony .","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"The committee ' s 10 Democrats are calling on Trump to either withdraw the nomination","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"or order the FBI to do a thorough investigation of the allegations .","depth":7},{"id":199,"text":"A second woman , Deborah Ramirez of Colorado , claims","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"Kavanaugh exposed himself to her at a drunken party","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"when they were freshmen at Yale University .","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"And in the most lurid allegation yet , Julie Swetnick of Washington said in a sworn statement","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"released Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"that Kavanaugh took part in efforts during high school","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"to get girls intoxicated","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"so that a group of boys could have sex with them .","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"In a transcript of an interview with Senate investigators","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"released Wednesday night ,","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"Kavanaugh said","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"Ramirez ' s allegation `` sounds like an orchestrated hit","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"to take me out . ''","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"He rejected Swetnick ' s claim in a statement Wednesday as `` ridiculous and from the Twilight Zone . ''","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"Republicans hold a 51-49 advantage in the Senate","depth":5},{"id":214,"text":"and can ' t afford more than one defection","depth":6},{"id":215,"text":"to ensure confirmation","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"without Democratic support .","depth":7},{"id":217,"text":"Several GOP lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"who remain publicly undecided","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"- most notably Alaska ' s Lisa Murkowski , Maine ' s Susan Collins and Arizona ' s Jeff Flake -","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":221,"text":"they want to hear what Ford has to say","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"before making up their minds .","depth":8},{"id":223,"text":"Flake sits on the Judiciary Committee","depth":7},{"id":224,"text":"and will have a chance","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"to question Ford and Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"Ford testified first ,","depth":7},{"id":227,"text":"giving an opening statement before questions by senators and by Mitchell ,","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"hired by the panel ' s 11 all-male Republicans","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"to handle their questioning .","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"Then Kavanaugh will do the same .","depth":6},{"id":231,"text":"Capitol police imposed strict security measures","depth":6},{"id":232,"text":"to keep protesters at bay","depth":6},{"id":233,"text":"after about 70 people were arrested each day during Kavanaugh ' s earlier hearing .","depth":5},{"id":234,"text":"At Ford ' s request , the hearing is being held in a smaller room with less space for media and the public .","depth":6},{"id":235,"text":"Protesters are being kept off that floor of the office building .","depth":6},{"id":236,"text":"Among those attending was actress Alyssa Milano , an activist in the `` Me Too '' movement .","depth":5},{"id":237,"text":"Seating Kavanaugh on the nation ' s top court","depth":6},{"id":238,"text":"- or not seating him -","depth":6},{"id":239,"text":"could affect the fight for control of Congress in the Nov. 6 election .","depth":5},{"id":240,"text":"Republicans are looking for Kavanaugh to cement a conservative majority on the court ,","depth":5},{"id":241,"text":"while Democrats say","depth":6},{"id":242,"text":"he could provide the fifth vote","depth":7},{"id":243,"text":"to overturn the Roe v. Wade decision","depth":8},{"id":244,"text":"that legalized abortion .","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"According to an NPR/PBS NewsHour/Marist poll","depth":6},{"id":246,"text":"released Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":247,"text":"59 percent of Americans think","depth":6},{"id":248,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":249,"text":"if Ford ' s accusation is true ,","depth":8},{"id":250,"text":"Kavanaugh shouldn ' t be confirmed .","depth":8},{"id":251,"text":"The poll found","depth":5},{"id":252,"text":"that 32 percent of the people","depth":8},{"id":253,"text":"who responded","depth":8},{"id":254,"text":"believe Ford ,","depth":7},{"id":255,"text":"26 percent believe Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":256,"text":"and 42 percent are unsure whom to believe .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":513,"left":469,"right":512,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":469,"left":429,"right":468,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":429,"left":330,"right":428,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":330,"left":277,"right":329,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":268,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":263,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"}